\frametitle{Interactive plots - Hover over plot}

In the file \verb|ui.R|:

\begin{exampleblock}{}
\begin{BVerbatim}
plotOutput("plot",
           hover = hoverOpts(id = "plot_hover",
                             delayType = "throttle")
)
\end{BVerbatim}
\end{exampleblock}{}

\vspace{1em}

In the file \verb|server.R|:

\begin{exampleblock}{}
\begin{BVerbatim}
output$plot_hoverinfo <- renderPrint({
  cat("Hover (throttled):\n")
  str(input$plot_hover)
})
\end{BVerbatim}
\end{exampleblock}{}

